body.p: This model is an implementation of the model described in a preprint by Giordano et al. arXiv:2003.09861v1

This model replicates exactly the results of Fig 3A-D of the paper. Note that in the paper they consider the inital time as day 1, where this model treats it as day 0, so the time axis is shifted by one day.

rdf:Description.dcterms:description: Giordano et al 2020 A SIDARTHE Model of COVID-19 Epidemic in Italy
